{"tid":1868584,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"醫護罷工你咩都做唔到 咁小野你做到啦掛","createTime":"2020-02-07T16:09:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T03:11:12.000Z","uid":256266,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"572b4d23c072ac72f8fc9a227b8d1abc0f70e6e9","tid":1868584,"uid":256266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T16:09:57.000Z","msg":"事緣我今晚咁岩聽到我阿媽聽緊YouTube 聽落去把聲有文有路咁 但仔細聽一聽 哇屌你老母醫護逃兵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申我媽就黃嘅 係佢啲藍朋友send俾佢<br />\n咁我就問一問個名好奇咁禁入去<br />\n哇 今日先出冇耐 我勁多like勁多view<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下面嘅留言仲要勁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家醫護罷工你哋咩都做唔到<br />\n起碼你哋可以幫佢哋維護下聲譽<br />\n係呢度嘈  不如慳返啲力入去嗰度同佢哋嘈<br />\n大家可以舉報佢個Channel 做到陳怡咁摺埋<br />\n係屋企出唔到嚟 可唔可以發展我哋嘅所長 喺嗰度踩場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n網絡私了佢哋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冷氣軍師你哋有用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另類行動post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好再喺度互相指責比五毛分化<br />\n可能啲五毛又會喺度留言 屌佢哋有咩用 咁佢哋自己喺度自hi 好過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁你就唔好喺度屌自己人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上熱門 整死個仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BxaF5SE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBxaF5SE.png&h=41712bf